      <title>Software Development Methodology</title>
      <link>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/software-development--engineering/fundamentals/sdlc/methodologies/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Jun 2025 06:22:00 +0000</pubDate>
